  <billdetail>
    <title>Te Pire Tuku i a Mauao hei Whenua Rāhui Hītori</title>
    <billtype>He Pire Kāwanatanga</billtype>
    <repnote>Te pūrongo nā te Komiti Whiriwhiri Take Māori i whakatakoto</repnote>
    <commentary id="DLM1235900" in.amend="false" irdnumbering="no" official="yes" bill.no="179" bill.type="government" stage="2" year="2008">
      <heading>Ngā Kōrero</heading>
      <comm.lev1>
        <heading>Tūtohutanga</heading>
        <para>
          <text>Kua ārohitia te Pire Tuku i a Mauao hei Whenua Rāhui Hītori e te Komiti Whiriwhiri Take Māori me te tūtohu kia whakamanatia tae atu ki ngā whakatikatika kua whakaaturia.</text>
        </para>
      </comm.lev1>
      <comm.lev1>
        <heading>Kupu whakataki</heading>
        <para>
          <text>Whakamana ai te Pire Tuku i a Mauao hei Whenua Rāhui Hītori i tētahi whakaaetanga nā te Karauna, nā Ngāi Te Rangi, nā Ngāti Ranginui, nā Ngāti Pūkenga, nā ngā kaitiaki o te Kaitiaki o Mauao me Waitaha hoki i haina i te marama o Here-turi-kōkā 2007. Hoatu wāhi ai te pire mō te whakawhitinga o te pānga angiangi i te whenua rāhui hītori o Mauao e mōhiotia nei ko Mount Maunganui, ko Mauao rānei, atu i te Karauna ki ngā kaitiaki o te Kaitiaki o Mauao mā rātou e tiaki mō Ngāi Te Rangi, Ngāti Ranginui me Ngāti Pūkenga hoki.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>I te mea kāore he wāhi i roto i te Ture mō ngā Whenua Rāhui o te tau 1977 (Reserves Act 1977) mō te whakawhiti āhua pēnei, ka hiahiatia he hanganga ture whakamana. Whakaae ai te whakawhitinga i te hiranga motuhake o Mauao ki te tangata whenua i Tauranga Moana. Hoatu wāhi ai te pire kia haere tonu ai a Mauao hei whenua rāhui hītori e ai ki ngā herenga o te Ture mō ngā Whenua Rāhui o te tau 1977 e whakamaru rā i a Mauao i ngā āhuatanga mahimoni, i te whakawehenga mai rānei i a ia i ōna rangatira. I runga i ngā whakaritenga i whakaaetia i te taha o ngā kohinga, ka puria anōtia hoki e te pire ngā whiriwhiringa o te rōpū whakahaere e tū nei mō Mauao. Kāore he wāhi o te pire i roto i tētahi whakataunga o te Tiriti, ko tāna kē he āwhina i te mahi whakatū hononga pai i waenganui i te Karauna, te iwi o Tauranga Moana me Waitaha hoki.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>I roto i tā mātou ārohitanga o te pire, ka whakatau mātou koia pū te āhua o te whakahokinga o te whenua i whakapuakina rā i te rara 7 o te pire, ā, me haere tonu te whakahaere tahi o te whenua rāhui e te Kaitiaki o Mauao me te Kaunihera o te Tāone nui o Tauranga.</text>
        </para>
      </comm.lev1>
      <comm.lev1>
        <heading>Ngā tika, ngā herenga hoki o te rangatiratanga</heading>
        <para>
          <text>Ka tūtohu mātou kia whakakorea ngā rara te 7 me te 8 o te pire, me te komokomo i te koronga o rara 7 ki roto i te rara hou 8.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>He maha tonu ngā tāpaetanga whakahē i te rara 7 i whiwhi i a mātou. Ko te nuinga i whakapuaki māharahara mō te kore hoatu wāhi whakahokinga a taua rara i te rangatiratanga katoa o Mauao ki te iwi, ā, mōrihariha rawa ana ngā kupu o taua rara, me te mea nei e whakapae ana, ko te ingoa anake tērā o te whenua e whakahokia ana, ko ngā tika katoa i kō atu e toe mai ana, kei te Karauna tonu ērā e mau ana.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>I raro i te Ture mō ngā Whenua Rāhui o te tau 1977, he tūranga whenua rāhui hītori tō Mauao. E toru ngā porohanga whenua kei roto i a Mauao, he whenua Karauna katoa, ā, kei te Karauna, kei te Minita rānei mō ngā Take ki Te Papa Atawhai ētahi mana, kawenga, herenga hoki ki aua whenua. Ka uru atu ki ngā mana o te Minita mō ngā Take ki Te Papa Atawhai, tērā e pā ana ki te whakaingoa rangatōpū whakahaere, pupuri hoki i te whenua rāhui e ai ki ngā wāhanga o te Ture mō ngā Whenua Rāhui o te tau 1977.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>Ka hiahiatia he rara ki roto i te pire kia āta kitea ai, i te mea hoatu wāhi ai te whakaaetanga kia whakaurua he hanganga ture tuku e mea ana, kei te haere tonu te pā o ngā ture whānui katoa ki a Mauao whai muri i te tukunga. Ko tā te rara e whai nei, kia noho tonu ngā tika, ngā herenga i raro me kī, i te hanganga ture mō te hauora me te whakatūpato, te whakatū whare me te tāke taunahatanga hoki, hei pīkautanga mā te Karauna. Hēoi, mā te hanga a te Karauna i ētahi tika, herenga hoki i kō atu, kāore a ia e mōhio ko ēhea ture ka whakamanatia ā meake nei ka pā ki ngā rangatira o Mauao. I raro i te wāhanga e tū nei o te pire, ehara mā rātou te mahi kawe i tētahi herenga rangatiratanga o te wā nei, ā meake nei rānei. Ki te tangohia katoatia a rara 7, he tino rangirua nui ka ara ake mō ngā herenga hei kawe pea mā ngā kaitiaki, ā, mō ngā tika pea kei a rātou mehemea he rangatira hoki rātou mō Mauao.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>Kei te whakaae mātou ki te hara ka puta ake nā ngā kupu taketake o rara 7, ā, nā reira ka tūtohu kia tuhia anōtia ngā kupu koronga i rara 8 hei whai ake i te māharahara nei. Ka tūtohu anō hoki mātou ki ngā whakatikatika whai ake mō rara 5 mehemea he herenga a tekiona 5 ki tekiona 8, ā, ki rara 10 hoki mō te whakakorenga o rara 7.</text>
        </para>
      </comm.lev1>
      <comm.lev1>
        <heading>Ngā whakatikatika paku nei</heading>
        <para>
          <text>Ka tūtohu whakatikatika mātou ki te whakamāramatanga mō te whenua rāhui hītori o Mauao i rara 3 kia whakaurua te whakamōhiotanga i whakapuakina a Mauao hei whenua rāhui hītori e te pānui a te <emphasis style="italic">Kāhiti </emphasis>o te tau 1981 i Pukapuka lll, whārangi 3065<emphasis style="italic">. </emphasis>Ka tūtohu whakatikatika whai muri anō hoki mātou ki te whakamāramatanga o te whenua rāhui i Tāpiritanga 1.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>Ka tūtohu mātou kia whakatikaina a rara 15(1) kia tono ko te Minita mō ngā Take Māori me tautuku ki ngā tekiona iti a (2) me (3) kāpā, ko te Minita mō ngā Take ki Te Papa Atawhai nā te mea kua whakaae te Minita mō ngā Take Māori ki te kawe i te mahi e pā ana ki te rēhita mō te rorohiko korehere.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>Ka tūtohu mātou kia whakatikaina a Tāpiritanga 2, kia hoatu mokamoka ai mō ngā taumahatanga ki te whenua rāhui hītori o Mauao kia āta mārama ai te mea mai a te pire, ko ngā tika ērā kei te Kaunihera o te Tāone nui o Tauranga e pupuri ana.</text>
        </para>
      </comm.lev1>
      <comm.lev1>
        <heading>Te whakahaerenga tahi i te whenua rāhui hītori o Mauao</heading>
        <para>
          <text>He huhua tonu ngā kaiwhakatakoto tāpaetanga i whakaputa whakaaro mō te take e pā ana ki te whakahaerenga tahi i te whenua rāhui hitori o Mauao e te Kaunihera o te Tāone nui o Tauranga me te iwi o Tauranga Mōana, me ētahi anō hoki e tūtohu ana kia whakatikaina te pire kia hoatu wāhi ai mō te whakahaerenga tahi o Mauao e te kaunihera me te iwi.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>Kua kite mātou kua whakaae te Kaunihera o te Tāone nui o Tauranga me te iwi o Tauranga Moana, he whakaaturanga arotau kei waenganui i a rātou, ko ērā hoki ngā tūmanako o te iwi e pā ana ki a Mauao.</text>
        </para>
        <para>
          <text>Kei waho te whakahaerenga tahi i te whenua rāhui hītori o Mauao i te hōkai tuku whakaaetanga me te pire. I raro i te Ture mō ngā Whenua Rāhui o te tau 1977, kei te Minita mō ngā Take ki Te Papa Atawhai te mana mō te whakaingoa rangatōpū whakahaere mō te whenua rāhui hītori o Mauao. Ka taea pea e tēnei wāhanga ngā kaitiaki mō te Kaitiaki o Mauao te whakauru ā meake nei. Kei te kite mātou, kāore tēnei i whakaarotia i te wā i tuhia ai te pire nā tōna nohonga kē mai ki waho i te hōkai whakaaetanga whiriwhiringa. I te mea he tuhinga paihere kore mana te whakaaturanga arotau, kāore i tika kia whakaurua taua momo whakaaetanga ki roto hanganga ture.</text>
        </para>
      </comm.lev1>
      <comm.appendix>
        <heading>Tāpiritanga</heading>
        <comm.lev2>
          <heading>Hātepe komiti</heading>
          <para>
            <text>I tonoa mai te Pire Tuku i a Mauao hei Whenua Rāhui Hītori ki te komiti i te 11 o Hakihea 2007. Ko te 15 o Hui-tanguru te rā i kati ai ngā tāpaetanga. E 27 ngā tāpaetanga a ngā kohinga whai pānga me te hunga takitahi i whiwhi, i whakaaroarotia e mātou. I whakarongo mātou ki ngā tāpaetanga ā-waha e 17 i ngā whakawātanga i Te Whanga-nui-a-Tara me Tauranga.</text>
          </para>
          <para>
            <text>Nā Te Puni Kōkiri te whakamaherehere ki a mātou.</text>
          </para>
        </comm.lev2>
        <comm.lev2>
          <heading>Ngā mema o te komiti, ko</heading>
          <para>
            <text>Dave Hereora (Heamana)</text>
          </para>
          <para>
            <text>Tākuta Pita Sharples (Heamana Tuarua)</text>
          </para>
          <para>
            <text>Chris Finlayson</text>
          </para>
          <para>
            <text>Hōnore Tau Henare</text>
          </para>
